---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>SignalRoutes</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #f8f7f4; color: #1a1a1a;">
    
    <main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 20px;">
      
      <!-- HEADER -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; margin-bottom:30px;">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="SignalRoutes logo" style="width:60px; height:60px; object-fit:contain;" />
        <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:32px;">SignalRoutes</h1>
      </div>

      <p style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:10px;">
        Choose the signal. Take the right route.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom:40px; line-height:1.5;">
        SignalRoutes builds software that helps you cut through noise, focus on what matters, and move forward with clarity.
      </p>

      <!-- PRODUCTS -->
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:20px;">Products</h2>

      <!-- FounderRoutes -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:14px; margin-bottom:24px;">
        <img src="/founderroutes.png" alt="FounderRoutes logo" style="width:42px; height:42px; object-fit:contain;" />
        <div>
          <strong>FounderRoutes</strong><br />
          Build your business with clarity. Know what to do now—and what not to do.<br />
          <a href="https://founder-routes-app-rep-production.up.railway.app/">Visit FounderRoutes →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SpendScore -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:14px; margin-bottom:24px;">
        <img src="/spendscore.png" alt="SpendScore logo" style="width:42px; height:42px; object-fit:contain;" />
        <div>
          <strong>SpendScore</strong><br />
          Understand your money in real time. Build better habits without complexity.<br />
          <em>Launching April 1 on Google Play</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SourceBrief -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:14px; margin-bottom:24px;">
        <img src="/sourcebrief.png" alt="SourceBrief logo" style="width:42px; height:42px; object-fit:contain;" />
        <div>
          <strong>SourceBrief</strong><br />
          The news, distilled. What matters. What’s true. Nothing extra.<br />
          <em>Join waitlist (coming soon)</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ComplianceIQ -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:14px; margin-bottom:24px;">
        <div style="width:42px; height:42px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:20px;">
          ⚖️
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>ComplianceIQ</strong><br />
          Stay ahead of compliance without drowning in updates.<br />
          <em>Coming soon</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
      <h2 style="margin-top:50px;">What We Do</h2>

      <p style="line-height:1.6;">
        Every product we build solves the same problem at a different level:
      </p>

      <ul style="line-height:1.6;">
        <li>Information → SourceBrief</li>
        <li>Money → SpendScore</li>
        <li>Business → FounderRoutes</li>
        <li>Regulation → ComplianceIQ</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="font-weight:600; margin-top:20px;">
        Clarity first. Direction next.
      </p>

    </main>

  </body>
</html>
